  "detailed_description": "<strong>Video Distribution and Monetization</strong><br>You can distribute your game without permission, regardless of whether you are an individual or a corporation.<br>Please include the name of the game in the title of your video or stream.<br>This is optional, but we would appreciate it if you could include a link to your Steam page in the summary section or elsewhere.<br><br>We will not be liable for any damages caused by the video distribution of this game.<br>These guidelines are subject to change without notice.<br>ーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー<br>Place the panels on the ground and Guide the rabbit safely to the goal!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/43f574ff42048046f3d679f7f641de23.webp?t=1730099778\" width=15 height=16 /></span> <strong>Story</strong><br>Rabbits who were living in a peaceful forest,blown away by a big storm.<br>The pink rabbit, who was left behind, travels to the outside world to find his friends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/bb1d327c99b1880f59246837fd635d8f.avif?t=1730099778\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/99a1ab54e1de9f9760cfd1947a405e68.webp?t=1730099778\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>Basic Rules</strong><br>Place the panels on the ground so that the rabbit can reach the goal panel.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/8e470340444c87f5c23c62e2aa8a28ad.poster.avif?t=1730099778\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/8e470340444c87f5c23c62e2aa8a28ad.webm?t=1730099778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/8e470340444c87f5c23c62e2aa8a28ad.mp4?t=1730099778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/37e93fa372b3fb2b1f9618c5640e0946.poster.avif?t=1730099778\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/37e93fa372b3fb2b1f9618c5640e0946.webm?t=1730099778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/37e93fa372b3fb2b1f9618c5640e0946.mp4?t=1730099778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When placing panels, be careful to avoid encountering natural enemies such as bears and foxes.<br>To avoid encountering natural enemies , place panels while keeping an eye on the direction in which they are moving.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/2a1cba22d7de88f0a3ac1a9125aedf94.poster.avif?t=1730099778\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/2a1cba22d7de88f0a3ac1a9125aedf94.webm?t=1730099778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/2a1cba22d7de88f0a3ac1a9125aedf94.mp4?t=1730099778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/b4683665a74ba7749e96336a8fe60cb4.webp?t=1730099778\" width=16 height=16 /></span> <strong>Gathering Friends</strong><br>As the game progresses, you will find your straggler friends.<br>You can also play with your fellow rabbits by giving them carrots that you pick up on stage, and they can switch places with the pink rabbit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/48a1e118663447a1d40f2db3d7cd1abc.poster.avif?t=1730099778\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/48a1e118663447a1d40f2db3d7cd1abc.webm?t=1730099778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341900/extras/48a1e118663447a1d40f2db3d7cd1abc.mp4?t=1730099778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
